    <h3>About Us</h3>
    <p class="text-body">
        Connected for you
        We understand that it can be stressful making doctors appointments for all your medical needs.
        Here at Stac, we centralize all appointments. Our mission is to connect patients with their doctors in the easiest way possible. Become an organized patient with our services.

        *Patient information will only have to be submitted once and you are all set.
    </p>
