    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <p class="text-body">
        Sign up - Become a member with us and we will match a doctor with you depending on your medical needs and where you live. You only need to input your information once for all appointments i.e.  insurance information, medical history, and personal information. Use this same account to schedule and more.

        Schedule - We will provide you with a list of locations in the King County area where you can choose from. All areas that we cover will be in each location for an easier commute on you. After you schedule we are in contact directly with the main offices of each location. We remind you of your appointment times and more.

        Relax - Leave it up to us to organize your appointments. It is our mission to relieve the hassle of juggling multiple office phone numbers, locations and doctors information.
    </p>

